to fastsim (source root!)

./bin/ma5 -R
ma5>set main.fastsim.package = fastjet
ma5>set main.outputfile = test.lhe
ma5>import samples/output.hepmc 
ma5>submit

the output test.lhe will be at e.g.
ANALYSIS_2/Output/_defaultset/

