create analysis folder

https://indico.in2p3.fr/event/8680/session/4/contribution/32/material/slides/0.pdf

./bin/ma5 -e

///////////////////////////////////////
compile

cd MyAnalysis/Build
source setup.sh
make
make clean (optional)
make mrproper (optional)

samples are in input.txt

launch
./MadAnalysis5job input.txt




